snippet: Stacy Lewis had to share the lead with Na Yeon Choi at the HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore after Choi birdied the 18th hole in the third round.
abstract: Stacy Lewis and Na Yeon Choi share third-round lead at HSBC Women’s Champions in Singapore.
